    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>WELCOME TO LAKE FACADE!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You have arrived at the mysterious Lake Facade. A secluded tranquil spot, with some of the best fishing around!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Or so you've been told...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enter Lake Facade and enjoy your stay or try to solve its mysteries.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1887910/extras/6a6aa3aabcb7c158f489d39cc7eb0ff7.poster.avif?t=1728294511\" width=512 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1887910/extras/6a6aa3aabcb7c158f489d39cc7eb0ff7.webm?t=1728294511\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1887910/extras/6a6aa3aabcb7c158f489d39cc7eb0ff7.mp4?t=1728294511\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Spend your time:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Fishing 🎣</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Exploring the Lake 🗺️</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Talk to the locals 💬</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Uncover the history and secrets of the Lake 📜</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Become one with the Lake 🐙</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1887910/extras/3f2ae8fa5cb0b86602a7e91532f1331a.poster.avif?t=1728294511\" width=512 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1887910/extras/3f2ae8fa5cb0b86602a7e91532f1331a.webm?t=1728294511\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1887910/extras/3f2ae8fa5cb0b86602a7e91532f1331a.mp4?t=1728294511\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A retro style puzzle/adventure game about fishing, exploring and uncovering ancient horrors.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Heavily inspired by H.P. Lovecraft and other Lovecraftian mythos, blending elements into both the gameplay and story (Not just a Cthulhu squid monster).</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Open ended gameplay lets you choose how you want to progress with multiple endings.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But the end is just the beginning...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your actions leave a permanent effect on this world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Are you sure that's what you really want?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1887910/extras/fb41f9cb933d81c441596961606bd5d3.poster.avif?t=1728294511\" width=540 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1887910/extras/fb41f9cb933d81c441596961606bd5d3.webm?t=1728294511\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1887910/extras/fb41f9cb933d81c441596961606bd5d3.mp4?t=1728294511\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>This is the full version of Lake Facade. The original was made in 10 days for the DreadXP Dredge the Depths Jam.</strong></p>",
